description:
## Context

The landing page currently uses a 2D DOM-based atom flow visualization. Dave wants the atomization-in-progress section to look genuinely 3D and professional — Apple Silicon territory, not debug viz.

This ticket contains paste-ready code to replace the 2D viz with a Three.js WebGL 3D scene. Two blocks: HTML container + JS function.

**File:** `keiracom_landing.html` (v2.1 — mobile-fixed, secret-sauce-hidden version)

---

## Block 1 — HTML container

**Find:** the `<!-- Atom flow animation visual -->` block (around line 520, the div with `id="atom-canvas"` and `height: 320px`).

**Replace the entire block with:**

